data.description: Beautiful, cozy manufactured home, vaulted ceilings, upgraded flooring and appliances. 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in the wooded surroundings of LaPine, minutes from the LaPine State Park. 1.02 Acres, Large Shop, large doors, exceptional storage and loft area. RV Parking and Hook Up. Second storage shed, also on site. New water filtration system for the home. Must see to appreciate!
